<section class="container-xl text-center py-5 py-md-6 py-xl-7">
  <div class="row justify-content-center gy-0">
    <div class="col-xl-18 col-xxl-17">
      <h2>About Defense.com™</h2>
      <p class="lead mb-0">Defense.com™ is a leading global cybersecurity company, having provided cyber protection services to many Fortune 500 companies such as Dell, Google and Berkshire Hathaway.</p>
    </div>
