      <h3>Helping all members of staff, male or female</h3>
      <p class="lead mb-0">With Defense.com being an inclusive company, Mother Fit were also able to provide our service to their male employees, who could pass the benefits onto their partners. Even if not pregnant or postpartum, they were still able to enjoy a better all round quality of life by becoming healthier and happier using the various exercise programmes and well being advice provided.</p>
